  <brief_title>LTOT in COPD Patients With Moderate Chronic Hypoxemia and Chronic Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Long-Term Oxygen Therapy (LTOT) in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) Patients With Moderate Chronic Hypoxemia and Chronic Heart Failure (CHF)</official_title>
